{"analytics_identifier":"OT269","base_path":"/government/organisations/equality-and-human-rights-commission","content_id":"673fea70-eba1-4218-8d13-84aa9bbfd20c","description":"The Equality and Human Rights Commission (EHRC) monitors human rights, protecting equality across 9 grounds - age, disability, sex, race, religion and belief, pregnancy and maternity, marriage and civil partnership, sexual orientation and gender reassignment. EHRC is an executive non-departmental public body, sponsored by the Cabinet Office .","details":{"acronym":"EHRC","alternative_format_contact_email":"","body":"<div class=\"govspeak\"><p>The Equality and Human Rights Commission (EHRC) monitors human rights, protecting equality across 9 grounds - age, disability, sex, race, religion and belief, pregnancy and maternity, marriage and civil partnership, sexual orientation and gender reassignment.</p>\n\n<p><abbr title=\"Equality and Human Rights Commission\">EHRC</abbr> is an executive non-departmental public body, sponsored by the <a class=\"brand__color\" href=\"/government/organisations/cabinet-office\">Cabinet Office</a>.</p>\n</div>","brand":"cabinet-office","foi_exempt":false,"logo":{"crest":"single-identity","formatted_title":"Equality and Human Rights Commission"},"ordered_corporate_information_pages":[],"ordered_featured_documents":[],"ordered_featured_links":[],"ordered_promotional_features":[],"organisation_featuring_priority":"news","organisation_govuk_status":{"status":"exempt","updated_at":null,"url":"http://www.equalityhumanrights.com/"},"organisation_political":false,"organisation_type":"executive_ndpb","secondary_corporate_information_pages":"","social_media_links":[]},"document_type":"organisation","first_published_at":"2012-02-08T16:37:17+00:00","links":{"available_translations":[{"analytics_identifier":"OT269","api_path":"/api/content/government/organisations/equality-and-human-rights-commission","api_url":"https://www.gov.uk/api/content/government/organisations/equality-a